    "causal_summary": "The 028 campaign's external-memory-systems child (`007-memory-systems`, 22 iterations across Mem0 / Graphiti / Letta / Cognee) surfaced a bundle of **cheap ranking and extraction improvements** for the Spec-Kit Memory MCP, mostly mined from **Mem0** scoring/extraction plus two Cognee extraction-config wins. The Wave-0 implementation packet (030) shipped a different, determinism-and-correctness-first slate; **none of this bundle was implemented** — it is absent from 030 §14. These candidates therefore remain open work.",
